<article class="blog--container blog-preview">
<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2018/06/28/spring-cloud-stream-fishtown-m1-2-1-0-m1-release-announcement">Spring Cloud Stream Fishtown.M1 /2.1.0.M1 Release Announcement</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
